      <title>Time yet for Touch of the Cursed to be fixed yet?</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shadowknights&amp;message.id=5658#M5658</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Since with the TSS expansion we&amp;nbsp;received upgrades to Touch of the Cursed (innate lifetap AA), isn't it time it's been looked at and&amp;nbsp;been fixed?&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;"It's the first time we've heard of it!"&amp;nbsp; No, it was reported at least in December 2005, in this thread, only on the 2nd page: &lt;A href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shadowknights&amp;amp;message.id=5267" target=_blank&gt;http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shadowknights&amp;amp;message.id=5267&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;"But it's working just fine!"&amp;nbsp; Under some circumstances, it does indeed work.&amp;nbsp; Under other circumstances, it doesn't.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;"Can it be duplicated?"&amp;nbsp; Yes it can.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Condensed summary: this aa works in non-instanced zones, instanced zones using the /dzadd system, and LDoN instanced zones.&amp;nbsp; It does NOT work in /taskadd zones; with the following exception: if you bought an aa (ANY aa) while in the /taskadd instanced zone, Touch of the Cursed will fire.&amp;nbsp; If you did not purchase any aa's while in the zone, it will not fire in the entire six hours you might spend in that zone.&amp;nbsp; This seems to hold true for Creators, Lair of the Black Wing, Plane of Time, etc. etc. etc.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Since the TSS aa was made to be an extension of Touch of the Cursed (instead of the proposed new ability in beta, Touch of the Fallen), it extends a broken aa line.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Now, I will make one small disclaimer: I have not yet bought the TSS extensions to Touch of the Cursed yet.&amp;nbsp; But I do know that my existing rank 3 TotC isn't working still in /taskadd instanced zones since TSS release.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; That is, unless I purchased some AA during that instance.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;But the test is, log in a test SK with Touch of the Cursed 1, 2 or 3, or buy it beforehand; then&amp;nbsp;get a /taskadd instance, and check to see if it fires at all during melee.&amp;nbsp; If not, it's broken and needs to be looked at.&amp;nbsp; If it fires under these conditions, I'm out to lunch and apologize and/or need to try to post a tighter scenario of circumstances.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Thanks for reading.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Sep 2006 06:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
      <author>Klotar-SoF</author>
